281
00:28:13,692 --> 00:28:15,526
Yeah.

282
00:28:17,905 --> 00:28:19,989
Did they get hurt, too?

283
00:28:20,157 --> 00:28:22,158
Uh...

284
00:28:22,326 --> 00:28:24,285
yeah, yeah, they did.

285
00:28:27,414 --> 00:28:29,290
I'm sorry.

286
00:28:32,503 --> 00:28:34,379
Me, too.

287
00:28:42,429 --> 00:28:44,138
