00:41:32,740 --> 00:41:34,533
( grunting )

401
00:41:40,999 --> 00:41:42,249
( panting )

402
00:41:46,754 --> 00:41:49,089
I'm sorry. You okay?

403
00:41:49,257 --> 00:41:51,925
You all right?

404
00:41:52,093 --> 00:41:54,219
I'm never gonna let
anything happen to you.

